CI/CD pipeline automation for Simple Flask app in AWS ECS

Code resides in GitHub
App needs to be containerized using Docker
Containers to be stored in Docker Hub as registry (CodePipeline)
Container needs to be updated every time the app code changes, to reflect changes. 
CI/CD using AWS technology ( Git workflow actions tests and creates new image and pushes it into Container Registry using CodeCommit/CodePipeline)
Using ECS backed by Fargate, Containers need to be able to scale horizontally. Containers need to be run as a service inside ECS Cluster
App Container, S3 and Infrastructure logs need to go to CloudWatch. 
Expose ECS metrics in Cloudwatch

AWS Account credentials will be provided

